# Summary
The User Sessions chart in Amplitude enables analysis of session-based metrics like frequency, duration, and event counts within sessions, helping users understand engagement patterns through metrics such as total sessions, average length, time spent, and event distribution across different user segments.

# Keywords
- Session-based metrics
- Session length distribution
- Average session length
- Sessions per user
- Event counts within sessions
- Sessions Module
- Time spent per user
- Session duration filters
- Length distribution histogram
- Custom metric formulas for sessions